                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote scope="sole" xml:id="hand-1">
                                <p>The text was copied in a <term type="script">mixed
                                        minuscule</term> script, upright, in brown ink, with little
                                    variation in letter size.</p>
                                <p>Syllabic abbreviations are not used and superscript word endings
                                    do not appear. Breathings are angular, and mute <hi rend="italic">iota</hi> is absent.</p>
                                <p>Punctuation used includes the lower, middle and upper points and
                                    the lower and middle commas.</p>
                            </handNote>
